reviewText: This is a delightful and enlightening day-long journey in the lives of 2-year-olds. Adults and children alike will enjoy watching as these toddlers play, socialize, experiment and test their limits. They made me laugh and remember when my now grown daughter was two. Enjoy!
As a mother of a soon to be 2 year old I appreciate the knowledge this video shares.  I feel a little less apprehensive about going for the ride into the "terrible twos" with my son.
